title: Seward Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Kosher, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small cafe in the Seward neighborhood offering breakfast, lunch, dinner, and late night snacks. The menu is vegetarian and vegan with the option of adding or substituting organic meat on some dishes. Meat is cooked and stored separately from veg. Live music on occasion. Accepts local checks.
